hadiths[66]{hadithnumber,text}:
1080,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''chaar baaten Anbiyaon aur Rasoolon ki sunnat mein sey hain : hayaa karna , itr lagana , miswak karna aur nikah karna.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1081,"Hum Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath nikley , hum nojawan they, hamarey paas (shaadi waghera umoor (maamle) mein sey) kisi chiz ki taaqat na thi. to aap ney farmaya : ''aey nojawanon ki jamaat ! tumharey ooper padhi. nikah lazim hai, kyonkey ye nigah ko neechi karney wala aur sharmgaah ki hifazat karney wala hai. aur jo tum mein sey nikah ki istataat (taaqat) na rakhta ho to is par roze ka ehtimam zaruri hai, kyonkey roza uskey liye dhaal hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is sanad sey kaee logon ney isi ki tarah Aamash sey riwayat ki hai. 3- aur abu-Muaawia aur Muhaaribi ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Aamash an Ibraheem an Alqama an Abdullah an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai. 4- dono hadisein sahih hain."
1082,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bina shaadi ke zindagi guzarney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Akhzim ney apni hadees mein itna izafa kiya hai ke Qatada ney ye aayate-karima : (ولقد أرسلنا رسلا من قبلك وجعلنا لهم أزواجا وذرية) ''hum aap sey pehley kaee Rasool bhej chukey hain, hamney unhen biwiyan ata kin aur auladen'' padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Ash'as bin Abdul-Maalik ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (an Hasan an Saad bin Hisham an Aaysha an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 3- kaha jata hai ke ye dono hi hadisein sahih hain. 4- is bab mein Saad , Anas bin Malik , Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1083,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Usman bin Mazoon ko baghair shaadi ke zindagi guzarney ki ijazat nahin di, agar aap unhen iski ijazat dey detey to hum khassi ho jaatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1084,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tumhen koi aisa shakhs shaadi ka pegham dey, jiski deen-daari aur akhlaq sey tumhen itminan ho to us sey shaadi kar do. agar aisa nahin karogey to zamin mein fitna aur fasade-azeem barpa hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki is riwayat mein Abdul-Hameed bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai, isey Les bin Saad ney ba-tareeq : (ibne Ajlan an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mursalan ( منقطعاً ( riwayat ki hai (yani : ibne Vushema ka zikr nahin kiya hai). 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ka kehna hai ke Les ki hadees (qarib tar) hai, unhon (Bukhari) ney Abdul-Hameed ki hadees ko mehfooz shumar nahin kiya. 3- is bab meinAbu Hatim Muzni aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey hadeesen aai hain."
1085,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey paas jab koi aisa shakhs (nikah ka pegham ley kar) aaye , jiski Deen daari aur akhlaq sey tum mutmain ho to us sey nikah kar do. agar aisa nahin karogey to zamin mein fitna aur fasad barpa hoga padhi. logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar is mein kuchh ho? aap ney teen baar yehi farmaya : ''jab tumharey paas koi aisa shakhs aaye jiski deen-daari aur akhlaq sey tum mutmain ho to us sey nikah kar do. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Abu Hatim Muzni ko sharfe-sohbat (izzat ka sath) hasil hai, hum iskey ilawa un ki koi hadees nahin jantey jo unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho."
1086,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aurat sey nikah uski Deen daari, uskey maal aur uski khoobsurti ki wajeh sey kiya jata hai.  lekin tum dindaar (aurat) sey nikah ko lazim pakad lo padhi. tumharey dono haath khaak aalud hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Auf bin Malik, Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) , Abdullah bin Amr , aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey hadeesen aai hain."
1087,"Unhoney eik aurat key paas nikah ka pegham bheja , to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum usey dekh lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Muhammad bin Muslima , Jabir , abu-Humed aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain : isey dekhney mein koi harj nahin jab wo uski koi aisi chiz na dekhey jis ka dekhna haram hai. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur « أحرى أن يؤدم بينكما » key maana ye hain ke ye tum dono ke darmiyan mohabbat paida karney key liye ziyada munasib hai."
1088,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haram aur halal (nikah) key darmiyan farq sirf daf bajaney aur aelan karney ka hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muhammad bin Haatib ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- Muhammad bin Haatib ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha hai, lekin wo kam-sin bachchey they. 3- is bab mein Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) , Jabir aur Rabee binte Muawwiz (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1089,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''is nikah ka aelan karo, isey masjidon mein karo aur is par daf bajaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ye hadees gharib Hasan hai. 2- Esa bin Memun Ansari hadees mein zaeef qarar diye jatey hain. 3- Esa bin Memun jo ibne-Abi Najeeh sey tafseer riwayat kartey hain, bharosemand hain."
1090,"jis raat meri shaadi thi uski subah Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey yahaan tashrif laye. aap merey bistar par aisey hi bethey, jaisey tum (Khalid bin zakwaan) merey paas bethey ho. aur chhoti chhoti bachchiyaan daf baja rahi thin aur jo hamarey baap-dada mein sey jange-badar mein shaheed huye they unka marsiya ga rahi thin, yahan tak ke un mein sey eik ney kaha : hamarey darmiyan eik Nabi hai jo un chizon ko janta hai jo kal hongi, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey farmaya : ''ye na keh. wohi keh jo pehley keh rahi thi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1091,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam shaadi karney par jab kisi ko Mubarak-baad detey to farmatey : (بارك الله لك وبارك عليك وجمع بينكما في الخير)''Allah tujhey barkat ata karey, aur tujh par barkat nazil farmaai aur tum dono ko khair par jama karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
1092,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar tum mein sey koi apni biwi key paas aaye yani us sey sohbat karney ka irada karey aur ye dua padhey : « بسم الله اللهم جنبنا الشيطان وجنب الشيطان ما رزقتنا » ''Allah key naam sey , aey Allah ! to hamein shetan sey mehfooz rakh aur usey bhi shetan sey mehfooz rakh jo to hamein ata karey yani hamari aulad ko.''  to agar Allah ney unkey darmiyan aulad deney ka faisla kiya hoga to shetan usey koi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1093,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney shawwaal mein mujh sey shaadi ki aur shawwaal hi mein merey sath aap ney shabbe-zufaaf manaai, Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) apney khandan ki aurton ki rukhsati shawwaal mein ki janey ko mustahab samajhti thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey hum sirf Sauri ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Sauri Ismail bin Umayya sey riwayat kartey hain."
1094,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abdur-Rehman bin Auf key jism par zardi ka nishan dekha to puchha : ye kya hai? unhoney arz kiya : mainey eik aurat sey khajoor ki eik guthli soney ke iwaz shaadi kar li hai, aap ney farmaya : ''Allah tumhen barkat ata karey, waleema padhi. karo chahey eik hi bakri ka ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Aaisha , Jabir aur Zuhair bin Usman (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : guthli bhar soney ka wazan teen dirham aur tihai dirham wazan key barabar hota hai. 4- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : paanch dirham aur tihai dirham key wazan key barabar hota hai."
1095,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Safiya binte Hayi ka waleema Sattu aur khajoor sey kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1096,"Sufiyan sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai, aur kaee logon ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (ibne Uena, an Zohri , an Anas) riwayat ki hai lekin in logon ney is mein Wayl bin Dawud aur un ke betey ke waaston ka zikr nahin kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Sufiyan bin Uena is hadees mein tadlees (khayanat) kartey they. kabhi unhoney is mein (Wayl bin Dawud an Ibneh) ka zikr nahin kiya hai aur kabhi uska zikr kiya hai."
1097,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pehley roz ka khana haq hai, doosrey roz ka khana sunnat hai. aur teesrey roz ka khana to mehaz dikhawa aur numaish hai aur jo riyaakaari karega Allah usey uski riyaakaari ki saza dega. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees ko hum sirf Ziyad bin Abdullah ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain. aur Ziyad bin Abdullah bahut ziyada gharib aur munkir hadeesen bayan kartey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko suna ke wo Muhammad bin Aqba sey naqal kar rahey they ke Wakee kehtey hain : Ziyad bin Abdullah is baat sey bahut buland hain ke wo hadees mein jhoot bolen."
1098,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tumhen dawat di jaey to tum dawat mein aao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Abu-Hurera , Bara , Anas aur abu-Ayyub (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1099,"Abu-Shuaib naami eik shakhs ney apney eik gosht bechne wale ladkey key paas aa kar kaha : tum merey liye khana banao jo paanch aadmiyon key liye kafi ho kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key chehrey par bhook ka asar dekha hai, to usney khana tayyar kiya. phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko bulaney key liye aadmi bheja. to usney aap ko aur aap key sath jo log bethey they sab ko khaney key liye bulaya, jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (chalney key liye) uthey, to aap key peechhey eik aur shakhs bhi chala aaya, jo aap key sath us waqt nahin tha jab aap ko dawat di gaee thi. jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam darwazey par pahunchey to aap ney sahib-khana sey farmaya : ''humarey sath eik aur shakhs hai jo hamarey sath us waqt nahin tha, jab tum ney dawat di thi, agar tum ijazat do to wo bhi andar aa jaey?''  usney kaha : hamney isey bhi ijazat dey-di, wo bhi andar aa jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1100,"Mainey eik aurat sey shaadi ki phir main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, to aap ney puchha : ''Jabir ! kya tum ney shaadi ki hai?'' mainey kaha : ji haan ki hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kisi kanwari sey ya bewa sey?'' mainey kaha : nahin, ghair kanwari sey. aap ney farmaya : ''kisi  (kanwari) ladki sey shaadi kyon nahin ki, to us sey kheltaa aur wo tujh sey khelti '' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! (merey walid) Abdullah ka intiqal ho gaya hai, aur unhoney saat ya no ladkiyan chhodi hain, main aisi aurat ko biyah kar laya hun jo unki dekh bhaal kar sakey. chunanche aap ney merey liye dua farmaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab aur Kaab bin Ajra Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1101,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wali ke baghair nikah nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Aaisha , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , Imran bin Husain aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. (abu-Musa Ash-ari ki hadees par Muallif ka mufassal (tafseeli) kalam agley baab (silsile) mein aa raha hai)."
1102,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis aurat ney apney wali ki ijazat key baghair nikah kya to uska nikah batil hai, uska nikah batil hai, uska nikah batil hai, agar usney ussey dukhool kar liya hai to uski sharmgaah halal kar leney key iwaz uskey liye mehar hai, aur agar Auliya mein jhagda ho jaey to jiska koi wali na ho uska wali haakim hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Yahya bin Saeed Ansari, Yahya bin Ayub, Sufiyan Sory, aur kaee huffaze-hadees ney isi tarah ibne-Jurej sey riwayat ki hai, 3- abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki) pichli ( hadees mein ikhtilaf hai, usey Israel , shareek bin Abdullah , abu Awana , zuhair bin Muawiya aur Qais bin Rabee ney basanad (أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai, 4- aur asbaat bin Muhammad aur Zaid bin Hubab ney basanad ( يونس بن أبي إسحق an أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai, 5- aur abu-Ubaida Haddad ney basanad ( يونس بن أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat ki hai, is mein unhoney Abu-Is'haq key wastey ka zikr nahin kya hai, 6- neez ye hadees Yunus bin abi Is-haq sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai unhoney basanad (أبي إسحق an أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai, 7- aur Shoba aur Sufiyan Sory basanad (أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai ke '' wali key baghair nikah nahin hai'' , aur Sufiyan Sory key baaz talaamiza ney basanad (سفيان an أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an أبي موسى) riwayat ki hai, lekin ye sahih nahin hai. un logon ki riwayat , jinhoney b-tareeq : ( أبي إسحق an أبي بردة an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai ke '' wali key baghair nikah nahin '' merey nazdik ziyada sahih hai, kyonkey Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey un logon ka samaa, mukhtalif oqaat mein hai agar-che Shoba aur Sory Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat karney waley tamam logon sey ziyada pukhta aur mazbut hafizey waley hain phir bhi un logon ( yani Shoba o Sory key ilawa doosrey riwayaton ( ki riwayat ashbah ( qarib tar ( hai. isliye ke Shoba aur Sory dono ney ye hadees Abu-Is'haq sey eik hi majlis mein suni hai, (aur unkey ilawa riwayaton ney mukhtalif oqaat mein) uski daleel Shoba ka ye bayan hai ke mainey Sufiyan Sory ko Abu-Is'haq sey poochhtey suna ke kya aap ney abu-Barda ko kehtey suna hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wali key baghair nikah nahin?'' to unhoney kaha : haan ( suna hai ). ye is baat ki daleel hai ke Shoba aur Sory ka makhool sey is hadees ka samaa, eik hi waqt mein hai. aur Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey riwayat karney mein Israel bahut hi Suqa Raavi hain. Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi kehtey hain ke mujh sey Sory ki riwaayaton mein sey jinhen wo Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat kartey hain, koi riwayat nahin chhoti , magar jo chhoti hain wo sirf isliye chhoti hain ke mainey is silsiley mein Israel par bharosa kar liya tha, isliye ke wo Abu-Is'haq ki hadeeson ko b-tareeq atam bayan kartey they. aur is baab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadees : '' baghair wali key nikah nahin '' merey nazdik Hasan hai. ye hadees ibne-Jurej ney b-tareeq : (سليمان بن موسى ، an الزهري ، an عروة ، an عائشة ، an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم), padhi. neez usey hujjaaj bin irtaat aur Jaafar bin Rabeea ney bhi b-tareeq : (الزهري ، an عروة ، an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai. neez Zohri ney b-tareeq : (هشام بن عروة ، an أبيه عروة ، an عائشة ، an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi key misl riwayat ki hai. baaz muhaddeseen ney Zohri ki riwayat mein) jisey unhoney b-tareeq : (عروة an عائشة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai) kalam kya hai, ibne-Jurej kehtey hain : phir main Zohri sey mila aur mainey un sey puchha to unhoney uska inkar kya uski wajeh sey un logon ney is hadees ko zaeef qarar diya . Yahya bin Moin kehtey hain ke ibne-Jurej sey is baat ko Ismail bin Ibrahim bin aleh key ilawa kisi aur ney nahin naqal kya hai, Yahya bin moayan kehtey hain : Ismail bin Ibrahim bin Uleh ka samaa, ibne-Jurej sey nahin hai, unhoney apni kitabon ki tas-heeh Abdul-Majeed bin abdul-Azeez bin abi Rawad ki un kitabon sey ki hai jinhen Abdul-Majeed ney ibne-Jurej sey suni hain. Yahya bin Moin ney Ismail bin Ibrahim bin aleh ki riwayat ko jisey unhoney ibne-Jurej sey riwayat ki hai zaeef qarar diya hai. 8- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm ka amal is baab mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees « la نكاح إلا بولي » '' wali key baghair nikah nahin '' par hai jin mein umr , Ali , Abdullah bin Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) waghera bhi shamil hain, isi tarah baaz Tabe-een fuqaha sey marvi hai ke wali key baghair nikah durust nahin. un mein Saeed bin Musaiyab , Hasan Basri , Shureh , Ibrahim Nakhai aur umr bin abdul-Azeez waghera hain. yehi Sufiyan Sory , Auzaai , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1103,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' zina kaar hain wo aurten jo gawahon key baghair khud nikah kar leti hain ''. Yusuf bin Hammad kehtey hain ke Abdul-Aalaa ney is hadees ko kitabut-tafseer mein marfoo bayan kya hai aur kitabut-talaq mein isey unhoney moqufan bayan kya hai, marfoo nahin kya hai."
1104,"Saeed bin abi Aruba ney isi tarah ki hadees bayan ki hai lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya. aur yehi ziyada sahih hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai, 2- hum kisi ko nahin jantey jisney isey marfoo kya ho siwaye uskey jo abdul-a'alaa sey marvi hai unhoney Saeed bin abi Aruba sey aur Saeed ney Qatada sey marfooan riwayat ki hai, 3- aur Abdul-Aalaa sey Saeed bin abi Aruba key wastey sey ye moqufan bhi marvi hai. aur sahih wo hai jo ibne-Abbas key qol sey marvi hai ke baghair gawah key nikah nahin, khud ibne-Abbas ka qol hai, 4- isi tarah sey aur kaee logon ney bhi Saeed bin abi Aruba sey isi tarah ki riwayat moqufan ki hai, 5- is bab mein Imran bin Husain , Anas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 6- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log kehtey hain ke baghair gawah key nikah durust nahin. pehley key logon mein is silsiley mein koi ikhtilaf nahin tha lekin baad key ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney is mein ikhtilaf kya hai, 7- ehle-ilm mein is silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai jab eik doosrey key baad gawahi dey yani dono b-yak waqt majlis nikah mein hazir na hon to koofa key aksar ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke nikah usi waqt durust hoga jab aqd nikah key waqt dono gawah eik sath mojud hon, 8- aur baaz ehal Madina ka khayal hai ke jab eik key baad doosrey ko gawah banaya gaya ho to bhi jayez hai jab wo uska aelan kar den . ye Malik bin Anas waghera ka qol hai. isi tarah ki baat Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi kahi hai jo ehal Madina ney kahi hai, 9- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke nikah main eik mard aur do aurton ki shahadat jayez hai, ye Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
1105,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen namaz key tashahud aur hajat key tashahud ko) alag alag ( sikhaya , wo kehtey hain salaat ka tashahud ye hai : التحيات لله والصلوات والطيبات السلام عليك أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله'' tamam zabani , badani aur maali Ibadatein Allah hi key liye hain. aey Nabi : salamti ho aap par aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkaten hon۔ salamti ho hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Allah key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain'' , aur hajat ka tashahud ye hai : إن الحمد لله نستعينه ونستغفره ونعوذ بالله من شرور أنفسنا وسيئات أعمالنا فمن يهده الله فلا مضل له ومن يضلل فلا هادي له وأشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله'' sab taarifein Allah hi key liye hain, hum usi sey madad chahtey hain aur usi sey maghfirat talab kartey hain, hum apney dilon ki shararaton aur burey aamal sey Allah ki panah maangtey hain, jisey Allah hidayat dedey usey koi gumrah karney wala nahin aur jisey gumrah kar dey , usey koi hidayat deney wala nahin. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin. main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Allah key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain''. aur phir aap teen aayaten padhtey. Absar (Raavi hadees) kehtey hain : to hamen Sufiyan Sory ney bataya ke wo teeno aayaten ye thi : يا أيها الذين آمنوا اتقوا الله حق تقاته wala تموتن إلا وأنتم مسلمون'' aey eman walo ! Allah sey daro jaisa darney ka haq hai aur haalate-Islam hi mein maro '' ( Aale-Imran : 102), واتقوا الله الذي تساءلون به والأرحام إن الله كان عليكم رقيبا''Allah sey daro, jis key naam sey tum sawal kartey ho aur jis key wastey sey natey jodtey ho, bilashuba Allah tumhara nigehban hai'' (Nisa ( , « يا أيها الذين آمنوا اتقوا الله وقولوا قولا سديدا » '' aey eman walo ! Allah sey daro, aur raast aur pakki baat kaho '' ( Ahzab : ۷۰ ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- isey Aamash ney b-tareeq : أبي إسحق an أبي الأحوص an عبد الله an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلمriwayat kya hai. neez usey Shoba ney b-tareeq : أبي إسحق an أبي عبيدة an عبد الله an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم riwayat kya hai, aur ye dono tareeq sahih hain, isliye ke Israel ney dono ko jama kar diya hai, yani (عن أبي إسحق an أبي الأحوص وأبي عبيدة an عبد الله بن Masood (Raziallahu anhu) an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) , 3- is bab mein Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke nikah baghair khutbey key bhi jayez hai. ehle-ilm mein sey Sufiyan Sory waghera ka yehi qol hai."
1106,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aisay sabhi khutbey jis mein tashahud na ho us haath ki tarah hain jis mein kodh ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
1107,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' shohar wali aurat chahey bewa ho ya mutallaqa ka nikah na kya jaey jab tak ke uski raza-mandi padhi. hasil na kar li jaey, aur kanwari padhi. aurat ka nikah na kya jaey jab tak ke uski ijazat na ley li jaey aur uski ijazat khamoshi hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umar, ibne-Abbas , Aaisha aur Urs bin Umaira (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke shohar wali ka nikah uski raza-mandi hasil kiye baghair nahin kya jaeyga. agar uskey baap ney uski shaadi uski raza-mandi key baghair kar di aur usey wo napasand ho to tamam ehle-ilm key nazdik wo nikah mansookh ho jaeyga, 4- kanwari ladkiyon key baap un ki shaadi un ki ijazat key baghair kar den to ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. koofa waghera key aksar ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke baap agar kanwari ladki ki shaadi uski ijazat key baghair kar dey aur wo baligh ho aur phir wo apney walid ki shaadi par razi na ho to nikah mansookh ho jaeyga 5- aur baaz ehal Madina kehtey hain ke kanwari ki shaadi agar baap ney kar di ho to durust hai bhale hi wo usey napasand ho, ye Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
1108,"shohar wali aurat apney aap par apney wali sey ziyada istehqaaq rakhti hai padhi. aur kanwari sey bhi ijazat talab ki jaeygi aur uski ijazat uski khamoshi hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shoba aur Sory ney isey Malik bin Anas sey riwayat kya hai, 3- baaz logon ney baghair wali key nikah key jawaz par isi hadees sey daleel li hai. halanke is hadees mein aisi koi chiz nahin hai jo uski daleel baney . isliye ke ibne-Abbas sey kaee aur turq sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wali key baghair nikah durust nahin ''. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad ibne-Abbas ney bhi yehi fatwa diya ke wali key baghair nikah durust nahin, 4- aur الأيم أحق بنفسها من وليها ka matlab aksar ehle-ilm key nazdik ye hai ke wali shohar wali ka nikah uski raza-mandi aur us sey mashwara key baghair na kerey. agar usney aisa kya to Khansa binte khuddam ki hadees ki mutabiq nikah khatm ho jaeyga. unkey walid ney unki shaadi kar di, aur wo shohar deeda aurat thin, unhen ye shaadi napasand hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unkey nikah ko fasakh kar diya ."
1109,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' yatim ladki sey uski raza-mandi hasil ki jaeygi, agar wo khamosh rahi to yehi uski raza-mandi hai, aur agar usney inkar kya to us par) zabardasti karney ka ( koi jawaz nahin ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa , ibne-Umar , aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- yatim ladki ki shaadi key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ney ikhtilaf kya hai. baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai : yatim ladki ki jab shaadi kar di jaey to nikah maqoof rahega . yahan tak ke wo baligh ho jaey . jab wo baligh ho jaeygi, to usey nikah ko baqi rakhney ya usey fasakh kar deney ka ikhtiyar hoga . yehi baaz Tabe-een aur deegar ulama ka bhi qol hai, 4- aur baaz kehtey hain : yatim ladki ka nikah jab tak wo baligh na ho jaey, durust nahin aur nikah mein « khiyaar » jayez nahin, aur ehle-ilm mein sey Sufiyan Sory , Shafai waghaira ka yehi qol hai, 5- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke jab yatim ladki no saal ki ho jaey aur uska nikah kar diya jaey, aur wo is par razi ho to nikah durust hai aur baligh honey key baad usey ikhtiyar nahin hoga . un dono ney Aaisha ki is hadees sey daleel li hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jab unkey sath shabe-zufaaf manaai, to wo no baras ki thin . aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ka qol hai ke ladki jab no baras ki ho jaey to wo aurat hai."
1110,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis aurat ki shaadi do wali alag-alag jagah kar den to wo un mein sey pehley key liye hogi, aur jo shakhs koi chiz do aadmiyon sey bech dey to wo bhi un mein sey pehley ki hui ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. is silsiley mein hamen ulama key darmiyan kisi ikhtilaf ka ilm nahin hai. do wali mein sey eik wali jab doosrey sey pehley shaadi kar dey to pehley ka nikah jayez hoga, aur doosrey ka nikah fasakh qarar diya jaeyga, aur jab dono ney eik sath nikah ( do alag alag shakhson sey) kya ho to dono ka nikah fasakh ho jaeyga. yehi Sory , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
1111,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo ghulam apney Malik ki ijazat key baghair shaadi kar ley, wo zaani hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- baaz ney is hadees ko basanad « Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Aqeel an ibne-Umar an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » riwayat kya hai, aur ye sahih nahin hai, sahih ye hai ke Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Aqeel ney Jabir sey riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hai, 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke Malik ki ijazat key baghair ghulam ka nikah karna jayez nahin . yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya waghera ka bhi qol hai, is mein koi ikhtilaf nahin ."
1112,Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis ghulam ney apney aaqa ki ijazat key baghair shaadi ki wo zaani hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1113,"bani Fazara ki eik aurat ney do jooti mehar par nikah kar liya , to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : kya to apni jaan o maal sey do jooti mehar par razi hai? usney arz kya : ji haan razi hon . wo kehtey hain : to aap ney us nikah ko durust qarar dey diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Abu-Hurera , Sehal bin Saad , abu Saeed Khudri , Anas , Aaisha , Jabir aur abu-Hadrad Aslami (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka mehar key silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai. baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : mehar is qadr ho ke jis par miyan biwi razi hon۔ ye Sufiyan Sory, Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, 4- Malik bin Anas kehtey hain : mehar eik chothai Dinar sey kam nahin hona chahiye, 5- baaz ehle-koofa kehtey hain : mehar das dirham sey kam nahin hona chahiye۔"
1114,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aurat ney aa kar arz kya ke mainey apney aap ko aap key liye hiba kar diya . phir wo kafi der khadi rahi (aur aap ney isey koi jawab nahin diya ( to eik shakhs ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! agar aap ko uski hajat na ho to us sey mera nikah kar dijiye . aap ney farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas mehar ada karney key liye koi chiz hai? '' , usney arz kya : merey paas merey us tehband key siwa kuch nahin hai. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar tum apna tehband usey dey dogey to tum baghair tehband key reh jaao gey, tum koi aur chiz talash karo '' , usney arz kya : main koi chiz nahin paa raha hun . aap ney ( phir ( farmaya : '' tum talash karo, bhaley lohey ki eik angoothi hi kyon na ho ''. usney talash kya lekin usey koi chiz nahin mili . to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tumhen kuch Quran yad hai? '' , usney kaha : ji haan , falan , falan Sura yad hai aur usney chand Suraton key naam liye to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney tumhari shaadi is aurat sey un Suraton key badley kar di jo tumhen yad hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shafai isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain. wo kehtey hain ke agar uskey paas mehar ada karney key liye koi chiz na ho aur wo Quran ki kisi Sura ko mehar bana kar kisi aurat sey nikah karey to nikah durust hai aur wo usey Quran ki wo Sura sikhaeyga, 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : nikah jayez hoga lekin usey mehar misl ada karna hoga . ye ehle-koofa , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
1115,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Safiya ko azad kya aur un ki azadi ko unka mehar qarar diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Safiya (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi hadees aai hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney uski azadi ko uska mehar qarar deney ko makrooh kaha hai, yahan tak ke uska mehar azadi key ilawa kisi aur chiz ko muqarrar kya jaey . lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1116,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen log hain jinhen dohra ajr diya jata hai : eik wo banda jo Allah ka haq ada karey aur apney Malik ka haq bhi, usey dohra ajr diya jata hai, aur doosra wo shakhs jiski milkiyat mein koi khoobsurat laundi ho, wo uski tarbiyat karey aur achi tarbiyat karey phir usey azad kar dey , phir us sey nikah kar ley aur ye sab Allah ki raza ki talab mein kerey. to usey dohra ajr diya jata hai. aur teesra wo shakhs jo pehley kitab ( Torat o Injeel ( par eman laya ho phir jab dusri kitab ( Quran Majeed ( aai to is par bhi eman laya to usey bhi dohra ajr diya jata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1117,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis shakhs ney kisi aurat sey nikah kya aur uskey sath dukhul kya to uskey liye uski beti sey nikah karna durust nahin hai, aur agar usney uskey sath dukhul nahin kya hai to wo uski beti sey nikah kar sakta hai, aur jis mard ney kisi aurat sey nikah kya to usney us sey dukhul kya ho ya na kya ho uskey liye uski maa sey nikah karna halal nahin hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sanad key aetbar sey sahih nahin hai, usey sirf ibne-Lahia aur Musanna bin Saleh ney Amr bin Shuaib sey riwayat kya hai. aur Musanna bin Saleh aur ibne-Lahia hadees key silsiley mein zaeef qarar diye jatey hain. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo kehtey hain ke jab aadmi kisi ki maa sey shaadi kar ley aur phir usey dukhul sey pehley Talaq dedey to uskey liye uski beti sey nikah jayez hai, aur jab aadmi kisi ki beti sey nikah karey aur usey dukhul sey pehley Talaq dedey to uskey liye uski maa sey nikah jayez nahin hai isliye ke Allah Taala ka irshad hai « وأمهات نسائكم » ( Nisa : ۲۳ ( , yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
1118,"Rifaa Qarzi ki biwi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : main Rifaa key nikah mein thi . unhoney mujhey Talaq dey di aur meri Talaq talaqe-bitta hui hai. phir mainey Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber sey shaadi kar li , unkey paas sirf kapdey key pallu key siwa kuch nahin hai padhi. , aap ney farmaya : '' to kya tum Rifaa key paas lot jana chahti ho? aisa nahin ho sakta jab tak ke tum un ( Abdur-Rehman ( ki lazzat na chakh lo aur wo tumhari lazzat na chakh lein '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Anas , Ramisa, ya Ghamisa aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke aadmi jab apni biwi ko teen Talaq dedey phir wo kisi aur sey shaadi kar ley aur wo doosra shakhs dukhul sey pehley usey Talaq dedey to uskey liye pehley shohar sey nikah durust nahin jab tak ke doosrey shohar ney us sey jima na kar liya ho."
1119,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney halala karney aur karaney waley par lanat bheji hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees maalul hai, 2- isi tarah Ash-as bin Abdur-Rehman ney basanad « جابر بن عبد الله an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم » riwayat ki hai. aur Aamir Shoby ney basanad مجالد an عامر an جابر بن عبد الله an علي riwayat ki hai, 3- is hadees ki sanad kuch ziyada durust nahin hai. isliye ke majaalid bin Saeed ko baaz ehle-ilm ney zaeef gardana hai. unhi mein sey Ahmed bin Hanbal hain, 4- neez Abdullah bin Numer ney is hadees ko basanad « Majalid an Aamir an Jabir bin Abdullah an Ali» riwayat ki hai, is mein ibn Numer ko weham huwa hai. pehli hadees ziyada sahih hai, 5- aur usey Mughira , ibne-Abi Khalid aur kaee aur logon ney basanad « الشعبی an الحارث an Ali » riwayat ki hai, 6- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Abu-Hurera , Aqba bin Aamir aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1120,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney halala karney waley aur karaney waley ( dono ( par lanat bheji hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee aur turq sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. jin mein umr bin Khattab , Usman bin Affaan , Abdullah bin umr waghaira (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain. yehi Tabe-een mein sey fuqaha ka bhi qol hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain, Wakee ney bhi yehi kaha hai, 4- neez Wakee kehtey hain : as-haab raey key qol ko phenk dena hi munasib hoga padhi. , 5- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : aadmi jab aurat sey nikah is niyat sey karey ke wo usey ( pehley shohar key liye ( halal kerega phir usey us aurat ko apni zojiyat mein rakh lena hi bhala malum ho to wo usey apni zojiyat mein nahin rakh sakta jab tak ke us sey naey nikah key zariey sey shaadi na kerey."
1121,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khaibar ki Fateh key waqt aurton sey mut'aa padhi. karney sey aur gharelu gadhon key gosht khaney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Sabra Juhni aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, albatta ibne-Abbas sey kisi qadr mut'aa ki ijazat bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, phir unhoney is sey ruju kar liya jab unhen Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key barey mein uski khabar di gaee. aksar ehle-ilm ka maamla mut'aa ki hurmat ka hai, yehi Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1122,"Mut'aa ibtadaaey Islam mein tha. aadmi jab kisi aisey shehar mein jata jahan uski jaan pehchan na hoti to wo apney qiyam ki muddat tak key liye kisi aurat sey shaadi kar leta. wo uskey saman ki hifazat karti . uski cheezen durust kar key rakhti. yahan tak ke jab aayate-karima : (إلا على أزواجهم أو ما ملكت أيمانهم) ''log apni sharmgahon ko sirf do hi jagah khol saktey hain, eik apni biwiyon par, doosrey apni matehet laundiyon par.''  nazil hui to ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : in do key ilawa baqi tamam sharmgaahen haram ho gaeen."
1123,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Islam mein na « جلب » hai, na « جنب  aur na hi « shighaar » , padhi. aur jo kisi ki koi chiz uchak ley , wo hum mein sey nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas, Abu Rihaana, ibne-Umar, Jabir , Muawiya , Abu-Hurera , aur Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1124,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nikahe-shighaar sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log nikahe-shighaar ko durust nahin samajhtey. 3- shighaar ye hai ke aadmi apni beti ka nikah kisi sey is shart par karey ke wo bhi apni beti ya behan ka nikah us sey kar dega aur unkey darmiyan koi mehar muqarrar na ho. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : nikahe-shighaar fasakh (radd) kar diya jaeyga aur wo halal nahin, agar-che baad mein unkey darmiyan mehar muqarrar kar liya jaey. ye Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 5- lekin Ata bin Abi Ribah kehtey hain ke wo apney nikah par qaaim rahengey albatta unkey darmiyan mehar muqarrar kar diya jaeyga, aur yehi ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai."
1125,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mana farmaya ke kisi aurat sey shaadi ki jaey aur uski phuphi ya uski khaala (pehley sey) nikah mein ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu Hareez ka naam Abdullah bin Husain hai.
1126,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mana farmaya ke aurat sey nikah kiya jaey jabke uski phuphi ( pehley sey) nikah mein ho ya phuphi sey nikah kiya jaey jabkey uski bhatiji ( pehley sey) nikah mein ho ya bhaanji sey nikah kiya jaey jabke uski khaala ( pehley sey) nikah mein ho ya khaala sey nikah kiya jaey jabke uski bhaanji pehley sey nikah mein ho. aur na nikah kiya jaey kisi chhoti sey jabke uski badi nikah mein ho aur na badi sey nikah kiya jaey jabke chhoti nikah mein ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. hamein inke darmiyan is baat mein kisi ikhtilaf ka ilm nahin ke aadmi key liye ye jayez nahin ke wo eik hi waqt mein kisi aurat ko uski phuphi key sath ya uski khaala ke sath nikah mein rakhey. agar usney kisi aurat sey nikah kar liya jabke uski phuphi ya khaala bhi uskey nikah mein ho ya phuphi sey nikah kar liya jabke uski bhatiji nikah mein ho to un mein sey jo nikah baad mein huwa hai, wo fasakh (radd) hoga, yehi tamam ehle-ilm ka qol hai. 3- Shaa'bi ney Abu-Hurera ko paya hai aur un sey) baraahe-raast ( riwayat bhi ki hai. mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : sahih hai. 4- Shaa'bi ney Abu-Hurera sey eik shakhs ke wastey sey bhi riwayat ki hai."
1127,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey ziyada puri kiye janey ki mustahiq wo shartein hain jin ke zariey tum ney sharmgahen halal ki hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. unhi mein umr bin Khattab bhi hain, wo kehtey hain ke jab kisi shakhs ney kisi aurat sey shaadi ki aur ye shart lagai ke wo usey uskey shehar sey bahar nahin ley jaeyga to uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo usey bahar ley jaey, yehi baaz ehle-ilm ka qol hai. aur Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi ke qaail hain. 3- albatta Ali bin Abi Talib sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney kaha : Allah ki shart yani Allah ka hukm aurat ki shart par muqaddam hai, goya un ki nazar mein shohar key liye usey uskey shehar sey bahar ley jana durust hai agar-che usney apney shohar sey usey bahar na ley janey ki shart laga rakhi ho, aur baaz ehle-ilm is janib gaey hain aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur baaz ehle-Koofa ka bhi qol hai."
1128,"Ghailaan bin Salma Saqafi ney Islam qubul kiya, jahiliyat mein un ki das biwiyan thin, wo sab bhi unkey sath Islam ley aayen, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen hukm diya ke wo un mein sey kisi chaar ko muntakhab kar (chun) lein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah isey Maamar ney basanad (Zohri an Salim bin Abdullah an ibne-Umar) riwayat kiya hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai. aur sahih wo hai jo Shuaib bin Abi Hamza waghera ney basanad :(الزهري an محمد بن سويد الثقفي) riwayat ki hai ke Ghelaan bin Salma ney Islam qubul kiya to unkey paas das biwiyan thin. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke sahih Zohri ki hadees hai jisey unhoney Salim bin Abdullah sey aur Salim ney apney walid Abdullah bin umr sey riwayat ki hai ke Saqeef key eik shakhs ney apni biwiyon ko Talaq dey di to umr ney us sey kaha : tum apni biwiyon sey ruju kar lo warna main tumhari qabr ko patthar maaroonga jaisey Abu Righaal ki qabr ko patthar maarey gaey they. 3- hamarey as-haab jin mein Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi shamil hain ke nazdik Ghelaan bin Salma ki hadees par amal hai."
1129,"Main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey Islam qubul kar liya hai aur merey nikah mein do behney hain? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum un dono mein sey jisey chaho muntakhab kar (chun) lo.''"
1130,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey Islam qubul kiya hai aur merey nikah mein do behney hain. aap ney farmaya : ''un dono mein sey jisey chaho , muntakhab kar (chun) lo.'' (aur dusri ko Talaq dey do.) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1131,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apni (mani) kisi ghair key bachchey ko na pilaey.'' (yaani koi laundi kisi aur se haamila ho to uske saath sohbat na kare jab tak ke wo is bachchey ko janm na dey dey.) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye aur bhi kaee turq sey Ruwaifi bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki gaee hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai. ye log kisi shakhs key liye ye jayez nahin samajhtey ke wo jab koi hamila laundi khareedey to wo us sey sohbat karey jab tak ke usey waza' hamal na ho jaey. 4- is bab mein Abu-Darda , ibne-Abbas , Arbaz bin Saariya aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1132,"hamney jange-autaas key din kuchh aurten qaid kin. aur un ki qom mein un aurton key shohar mojud they, logon ney iska zikr Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kiya to ye aayat nazil hui :(والمحصنات من Nisa إلا ما ملكت أيمانكم) ''tum par shohar wali aurten bhi haram hain siwaye iske ke wo tumhari milkiyat mein aa gaee hon.'' (Nisaa:24). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- isi tarah sey isey Sory ney ba-tareeq : (عثمان البتي an أبي الخليل an أبي سعيد) riwayat kiya hai."
1133,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kuttey ki qeemat padhi. , zaaniya ki kamai padhi. aur kaahin ki meethaee sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Raafey bin khadij , abu-Juhaifa , Abu-Hurera , aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1134,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi aadmi apney bhai ki bai (saude) par bai (sauda) na karey aur na koi apney bhai ke pegham par apna pegham bhejey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Samura aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Malik bin Anas kehtey hain : aadmi ke apney bhai ke pegham par apna pegham bhejney ki mumaaniat ka matlab ye hai ke aadmi ney kisi aurat ko pegham diya ho aur wo aurat us sey razi ho gaee ho, to kisi ke liye jayez nahin ke wo apney bhai key pegham par apna pegham bhejey. 4- Shafai kehtey hain ke is hadees ke aadmi apney bhai ke pegham par pegham na bhejey ka matlab hamarey nazdik ye hai ke jab aadmi ney kisi aurat ko pegham bheja ho aur wo aurat us sey razi ho gaee ho aur uski taraf maael ho gaee ho to aisi surat mein kisi key liye durust nahin ke wo uskey pegham par apna pegham bhejey, lekin uski raza-mandi aur uska milaan malum honey sey pehley agar wo usey pegham dey to is mein koi harj nahin hai. iski daleel Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu Anha) ki ye hadees hai ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar zikr kiya ke abu-Jahm bin Huzefa aur Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan ney unhen nikah ka pegham diya hai to aap ney farmaya : ''abu-Jahm ka maamla ye hai ke wo apna dandaa aurton sey nahin uthatey (yani aurton ko bahut maartay hain) rahey Muawiya to wo gharib aadmi hain un ke paas maal nahin hai, lihaza tum Usama bin Zaid sey nikah kar lo.'' hamarey nazdik is hadees ka mafhoom (aur Allah behtar janta hai) ye hai ke Fatima ney un mein sey kisi eik key sath bhi apni raza-mandi ka izhar nahin kiya tha aur agar wo uska izhar kar detin to usey chhod kar aap unhen Usama (Raziallahu anhu) sey nikah ka mashwara na detey."
1135,"Main aur abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman dono Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu Anha) ke paas aaye unhoney hum sey bayan kiya ke unkey shohar ney unhen teen Talaq dey di aur na unkey liye rihaaish ka intizam kiya aur na khaney peeney ka. aur unhoney merey liye das bori ghalla, paanch bori jau ke aur paanch gehun ke apney chacha zaad bhai ke paas rakh den, to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar aap sey iska zikr kiya, to aap ney farmaya : ''unhoney theek kiya, aur mujhey aap ney hukm diya ke main Umme shareek key ghar mein iddat guzaaron.''  phir mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Umme shareek ke ghar muhajrin aatey jatey rehtey hain. tum ibne Umme Maktoom key ghar mein iddat guzaaro.'' wahan ye bhi sahulat raheygi ke tum (sar waghera sey) kapdey utaarogi to tumhen wo nahin dekh paeyngey, phir jab tumhari iddat puri ho jaey aur koi tumharey paas pegham nikah ley kar aaye to mujhey batana, chunanche jab meri iddat puri ho gaee to abu-Jahm aur Muawiya ney mujhey pegham bheja. mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar aap sey iska zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''Muawiya to aisey aadmi hain ke un ke paas maal nahin, aur abu-Jahm aurton key liye sakht waqey huye hain.'' phir mujhey Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney pegham bheja aur mujh sey shaadi kar li. Allah Taala ney Usama mein mujhey barkat ata farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- isey Sufiyan Sory ney bhi abu-Bakar bin abi Jaham sey isi hadees ki tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur is mein unhoney itna izafa kiya hai ke mujh sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum Usama sey nikah kar lo.''"
1136,"hamney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum log azl padhi. kartey they, to yahudiyon ney kaha : qabr mein zinda dafn karney ki ye eik chhoti surat hai. aap ney farmaya : ''yahudiyon ney jhoot kaha. Allah jab usey paida karna chaheyga to usey koi rok nahin sakeyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein umr , Bara aur Abu-Hurera , abu Saeed Khudri Raziallahu anhum sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1137,Hum azl kartey they aur Quran utar raha tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees aur bhi kaee turq sey un sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney azl ki ijazat di hai. Malik bin Anas ka qol hai ke azad aurat sey azl ki ijazat li jaeygi aur laundi sey ijazat leney ki zarurat nahin.
1138,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas azl ka zikr kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi aisa kyon karta hai?'' ibne-Abi umr ney apni hadees mein ye izafa kiya hai : ''aur aap ney ye nahin kaha ke tum mein sey koi aisa na karey.''  aur un dono ney apni hadees mein ye bhi kaha hai ke ''jis jaan ko bhi Allah ko paida karna hai wo usey paida kar key hi rahega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye iskey ilawa aur bhi turq sey abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, 3- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney azl ko makrooh qarar diya hai."
1139,"agar main chahun to kahun ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya lekin unhoney sirf itna kaha : ''sunnat padhi. ye hai ke aadmi jab apni biwi key hotey huye kisi kanwari sey shaadi karey to uskey yahaan saat raat thehrey, aur jab ghair kanwari sey shaadi karey to uskey yahaan teen raat thehrey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Muhammad bin Is-haq ney marfoo kiya hai, unhoney basanad (Ayub an Abi Qulaba an Anas ( riwayat ki hai aur baaz ney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai. 3- is bab mein Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab aadmi apni biwi key hotey huye kisi aur kanwari sey shaadi karey, to uskey paas saat raat thehrey , phir uskey baad unkey darmiyan baari taqseem karey , aur pehli biwi key hotey huye jab kisi ghair kanwari  (bewa ya mutallaqa) sey shaadi karey to uskey paas teen raat thehrey. Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 5- Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha ke jab koi apni biwi key hotey huye kanwari sey shaadi karey to wo uskey paas teen raat thehrey aur jab ghair kanwari sey shaadi karey to uskey yahaan do raat thehrey. lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1140,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni biwiyon key darmiyan baari taqseem kartey huye farmatey : ''aey Allah ! ye meri taqseem hai jis par main qudrat rakhta hun, lekin jiski qudrat to rakhta hai, main nahin rakhta , iskey barey mein mujhey malamat na karna.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ko isi tarah kaee logon ney basanad :(حماد بن سلمة an أيوب an أبي قلابة an عبد الله بن يزيد an عائشة) riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam baari taqseem kartey they jabke isey Hammad bin Zaid aur doosrey kaee Suqaat ney basanad (Ayooban abi Qalaba) riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam baari taqseem kartey they aur ye Hammad bin Salma ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, aur ''jis ki qudrat to rakhta hai main nahin rakhta'' sey murad mohabbat aur muddat hai, isi tarah baaz ehle-ilm ney iski tafseer ki hai."
1141,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab kisi shakhs key paas do biwiyan hon aur unkey darmiyan insaf sey kaam na ley to wo qiyamat key din us haal mein aayega ke uska eik pehlu jhuka huwa hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko Hamaam bin Yahya ne Qatada sey musnadan padhi. riwayat kiya hai. 2- aur isey Hisham Dustwaai ney bhi Qatada sey riwayat kiya hai lekin is riwayat mein hai ke aisa kaha jata tha … 3- hum is hadees ko sirf Hamaam hi ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain aur Hamaam bharosemand Hafiz hain.
1142,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni ladki Zenab ko Abul-Aas bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) key paas naey mehar aur naey nikah key zariey lota diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad mein kuchh kalam hai aur dusri hadees mein bhi kalam hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka amal isi hadees par hai ke aurat jab shohar sey pehley Islam qubul kar ley, phir uska shohar iddat ke doran Islam ley aaye to uska shohar hi uska ziyada haqdaar hai jab wo iddat mein ho. yehi Malik bin Anas , Auzaai , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
1143,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni beti Zenab ko Abul-Aas bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) key paas chhe saal baad padhi. pehley nikah hi par wapis bhej diya aur phir sey nikah nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ki sanad mein koi shubah nahin hai, lekin hum is hadees mein naqad ki wajeh nahin jantey hain. shayad ye chiz Dawud bin Husain ki janib sey unkey hifz ki taraf sey aai hai."
1144,Eik shakhs Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke zamaney mein musalman ho kar aaya phir uski biwi bhi musalman ho kar aa gaee to usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! usney merey sath Islam qubul kiya tha. to aap usey mujhey wapis dey dijiye. to aap ney isey usi ko wapis dey diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- Hujjaaj ney ye hadees ba-tareeq :(عمرو بن شعيب an أبيه an جده) riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni beti Zenab ko Abul-Aas ke yahaan naey mehar aur naey nikah key zariey lotaya. 3- Yazeed bin Harun kehtey hain ke ibne-Abbas ki hadees sanad ke aetbar sey sab sey achchhi hai lekin amal (عمرو بن شعيب an أبيه an جده) ki hadees par hai.
1145,"Un sey eik aisey shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jisney eik aurat sey shaadi ki lekin usney na uska mehar muqarrar kiya aur na us sey sohbat ki yahan tak ke wo mar gaya, to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha is aurat key liye apney khandan ki aurton key jaisa mehar hoga. na us sey kam aur na us sey ziyada. usey iddat bhi guzaarni hogi aur meeras mein bhi uska haq hoga. to Maaqil bin Sanan Ash'jai ney khadey ho kar kaha : Birwaa binte Vaashiq jo hamarey qabiley ki aurat thi, ke barey mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisa hi faisla farmaya tha jaisa aap ney kiya hai. to is sey ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) khush huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jarrah sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Yazeed bin Harun aur Abdur-Razzaaq ney basanad (Sufiyaan an Mansoor) sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 4- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye aur bhi turq sey marvi (riwayat) hai. 5- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai padhi. yehi Sory , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 6- aur Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba kehtey hain : jin mein Ali bin abi Talib , Zaid bin Sabit , ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain kehtey hain ke jab aadmi kisi aurat sey shaadi karey, aur usney is sey abhi dukhul na kiya (sohbat na ki) ho aur na hi is ka mehar muqarrar kiya ho aur wo mar jaey to ye log kehtey hain ke is aurat ko meeras mein haq milega. lekin koi mehar nahin hoga padhi. aur usey iddat guzaarni hogi. yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai. wo kehtey hain : agar Birwaa binte Vaashiq ki hadees sahih ho to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi honey ki wajeh sey hujjat hogi. aur Shafai sey marvi hai ke unhoney baad mein Misir mein is qol sey ruju kar liya aur Birwaa binte Vaashiq ki hadees ke mutabiq fatwa diya."
